ke over..\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_toggle][tm_pb_toggle admin_label="Toggle" title="Business plan consulting" open="off" icon_color="#ffffff" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" open_toggle_background_color="#15c1c6" closed_toggle_background_color="#333333" title_font="Merriweather|on|||" title_text_color="#ffffff" body_font_size="16px" title_font_size="16px"]\r\n\r\nAre you about to pitch a plan for angel''s funding? Or you''ve started it all with your principal capital at stake? We can help to plan it all out.\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_toggle][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section][tm_pb_section admin_label="Section" fullwidth="off" specialty="off" transparent_background="on" allow_player_pause="off" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" custom_padding="||50px|" custom_padding_tablet="||30px|" custom_padding_last_edited="on|tablet" padding_mobile="off" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" width_unit="on" make_equal="off" use_custom_gutter="off"][tm_pb_row admin_label="Row" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" use_grid_padding="on" width_unit="on" custom_padding="||25px|" padding_mobile="off" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" make_equal="off" parallax_1="off" parallax_method_1="off" column_padding_mobile="on"][tm_pb_column type="4_4"][tm_pb_divider admin_label="Divider" color="#ebebeb" show_divider="on" divider_style="solid"] [/tm_pb_divider][tm_pb_text admin_label="Text" text_orientation="left" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" custom_margin="20px|||" custom_margin_last_edited="on|"]\r\n<h5>Tabs</h5>\r\n[/tm_pb_text][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label="Row" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" use_grid_padding="on" width_unit="on" padding_mobile="off" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" make_equal="off" parallax_1="off" parallax_method_1="off" column_padding_mobile="on"][tm_pb_column type="4_4"][tm_pb_tabs admin_label="Tabs" active_tab_background_color="#15c1c6" inactive_tab_background_color="#333333" tab_text_color="#ffffff" use_border_color="on" border_color="#ebebeb" border_style="solid" tab_font="Merriweather|on|||" tab_font_size="16" body_font_size="16" saved_tabs="all"] [tm_pb_tab title="Assessment" tab_font_select="default" tab_font="||||" tab_line_height="2em" tab_line_height_tablet="2em" tab_line_height_phone="2em" body_font_select="default" body_font="||||" body_line_height="2em" body_line_height_tablet="2em" body_line_height_phone="2em"]\r\n\r\nFirstly we received access to all documentation, reports and structure of the company. We analyzed the current and yearly performance, sales, staff flow for the hayford company... <img class="alignnone wp-image-1463 size-full" src="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image31.jpg" width="1098" height="586" />\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title="Business strategy" tab_font_select="default" tab_font="||||" tab_line_height="2em" tab_line_height_tablet="2em" tab_line_height_phone="2em" body_font_select="default" body_font="||||" body_line_height="2em" body_line_height_tablet="2em" body_line_height_phone="2em"]\r\n\r\nThe next step was to draft a business strategy for business'' future deelopment over a period of 2, 5 and 10 years. We always aim to correlate our recommendations with the vision each company offers, when we''re composing such a strategy... <img class="alignnone wp-image-1463 size-full" src="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image31.jpg" width="1098" height="586" />\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title="HR optimization" tab_font_select="default" tab_font="||||" tab_line_height="2em" tab_line_height_tablet="2em" tab_line_height_phone="2em" body_font_select="default" body_font="||||" body_line_height="2em" body_line_height_tablet="2em" body_line_height_phone="2em"]\r\n\r\nAn optimized business always starts with the team optimization. That is the reason we do the human resources diligence and file our suggestions to the board. <img class="alignnone wp-image-1463 size-full" src="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image31.jpg" width="1098" height="586" />\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title="Processes optimization" tab_font_select="default" tab_font="||||" tab_line_height="2em" tab_line_height_tablet="2em" tab_line_height_phone="2em" body_font_select="default" body_font="||||" body_line_height="2em" body_line_height_tablet="2em" body_line_height_phone="2em"]\r\n\r\nBusiness processes optimization is the most vital instrument when we aim to turn the company around. We always sketch and implement such overhauls in a close cooperation with company''s top management. <img class="alignnone wp-image-1463 size-full" src="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image31.jpg" width="1098" height="586" />\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title="Market research" tab_font_select="default" tab_font="||||" tab_line_height="2em" tab_line_height_tablet="2em" tab_line_height_phone="2em" body_font_select="default" body_font="||||" body_line_height="2em" body_line_height_tablet="2em" body_line_height_phone="2em"]\r\n\r\nBeing one of the most competitive out there, we had conducted multiple researches and we arranged an extensive overhaul for the marketing department of the company. <img class="alignnone wp-image-1463 size-full" src="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image31.jpg" width="1098" height="586" />\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title="Year-by-year analysis" tab_font_select="default" tab_font="||||" tab_line_height="2em" tab_line_height_tablet="2em" tab_line_height_phone="2em" body_font_select="default" body_font="||||" body_line_height="2em" body_line_height_tablet="2em" body_line_height_phone="2em"]\r\n\r\nAfter out initial job''s been implemented, the next thing we did is a year-by-year analysis. Since year one and during all 6 years we''ve been advising hayford company shown a significant surge both in sales and market value. <img class="alignnone wp-image-1463 size-full" src="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image31.jpg" width="1098" height="586" />\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_tab] [/tm_pb_tabs][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section][tm_pb_section admin_label="Section" fullwidth="off" specialty="off" transparent_background="on" allow_player_pause="off" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" custom_padding="||50px|" custom_padding_tablet="||30px|" custom_padding_last_edited="on|desktop" padding_mobile="off" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" width_unit="on" make_equal="off" use_custom_gutter="off"][tm_pb_row admin_label="Row" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" use_grid_padding="on" width_unit="on" custom_padding="||25px|" padding_mobile="off" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" make_equal="off" parallax_1="off" parallax_method_1="off" column_padding_mobile="on"][tm_pb_column type="4_4"][tm_pb_divider admin_label="Divider" color="#ebebeb" show_divider="on" divider_style="solid"] [/tm_pb_divider][tm_pb_text admin_label="Text" text_orientation="left" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" custom_margin="40px|||" custom_margin_tablet="20px|||" custom_margin_last_edited="on|tablet"]\r\n<h5>Contact form</h5>\r\n[/tm_pb_text][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label="Row" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" use_grid_padding="on" width_unit="on" padding_mobile="off" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" make_equal="off" parallax_1="off" parallax_method_1="off" parallax_2="off" parallax_method_2="off" column_padding_mobile="on"][tm_pb_column type="4_4"][tm_pb_contact_form admin_label="Contact Form" captcha="on" use_redirect="off" success_message="Your message was sent successflly. Thanks. " submit_text="send" form_background_color="#f6f6f6" input_border_radius="0" form_field_font_size="16" form_field_text_color="#9f9f9f" use_border_color="off" border_color="#fff