ather" header_font="Merriweather||||" body_font_select="default" body_font="||||" custom_button="off" button_font_select="default" button_font="||||" button_use_icon="default" button_icon_placement="right" button_on_hover="on" header_font_size="66" header_font_size_tablet="46" header_font_size_phone="36" header_font_size_last_edited="on|phone" header_text_color="#ffffff" body_text_color="#ffffff" body_line_height="1.4em" body_line_height_tablet="1.4em" body_line_height_phone="1.4em"]<p style="text-align: center;">We help you in creating a financial strategy that represents your personality. Getting to know you is financial advisor’s primary goal. - An approach centered around your life’s priorities. It’s time for a financial strategy that puts your needs and priorities front and center.</p>[/tm_pb_slide]\n\n[/tm_pb_slider][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row]', 'hayford_slider', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'hayford_slider', '', '', '2016-07-25 16:02:40', '2016-07-25 16:02:40', '', 0, 'your_website_url_here/tm_pb_layout/hayford_slider/', 0, 'tm_pb_layout', '', 0),
(1194, 1, '2016-07-26 08:44:26', '2016-07-26 08:44:26', '[tm_pb_row admin_label="Row" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" use_grid_padding="on" width_unit="on" padding_mobile="off" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" make_equal="off" parallax_1="off" parallax_method_1="off" parallax_2="off" parallax_method_2="off" parallax_3="off" parallax_method_3="off" parallax_4="off" parallax_method_4="off" column_padding_mobile="on" template_type="row"][tm_pb_column type="1_4"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label="Person" name="Damien Kaschzmarek" image_url="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/about-05.jpg" animation="off" background_layout="light" header_text_color="#333333" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" custom_margin="||50px|" header_font="Merriweather||||" header_font_size="26" header_line_height="1.3em" saved_tabs="all" text_alignment="left"]\n\n<p>Damien was appointed as Managing Director of our Investments venture in February 2014, after 4 years as Chief Executive Officer.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type="1_4"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label="Person" name="Derek Zoolander" image_url="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/about-06.jpg" animation="off" background_layout="light" header_text_color="#333333" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" custom_margin="||50px|" header_font="Merriweather||||" header_font_size="26" header_line_height="1.3em" saved_tabs="all" text_alignment="left"]\n\n<p>Derek joined us in 2007, has been Company Secretary since 2010 and was appointed Chief Operating Officer in 2015. He is a Chartered Accountant.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type="1_4"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label="Person" name="Tom Marvolo" image_url="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/about-07.jpg" animation="off" background_layout="light" header_text_color="#333333" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" custom_margin="||45px|" header_font="Merriweather||||" header_font_size="26" header_line_height="1.3em" saved_tabs="all" text_alignment="left"]\n\n<p>He has over 30 years’ experience in financial and investment accounting and has extensive experience in the management of the portfolio...</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type="1_4"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label="Person" name="James Potter" image_url="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/about-08.jpg" animation="off" background_layout="light" header_text_color="#333333" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" custom_margin="||50px|" header_font="Merriweather||||" header_font_size="26" header_line_height="1.3em" saved_tabs="all" text_alignment="left"]\n\n<p>Mr. Potter joined us in 2010 as an Investment Analyst and was promoted to Senior Investment Officer. He has long experience as an analyst.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row]', 'hayford_person', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'hayford_person', '', '', '2016-07-26 08:44:26', '2016-07-26 08:44:26', '', 0, 'your_website_url_here/tm_pb_layout/hayford_person/', 0, 'tm_pb_layout', '', 0),
(1196, 1, '2016-07-26 08:47:29', '2016-07-26 08:47:29', '[tm_pb_accordion admin_label="Accordion" toggle_font_size="16px" toggle_text_color="#ffffff" body_font_size="16px" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" closed_toggle_background_color="#333333" open_toggle_background_color="#2da5ee" open_toggle_text_color="#ffffff" closed_toggle_text_color="#ffffff" icon_color="#ffffff" saved_tabs="all" template_type="module"]\n\n[tm_pb_accordion_item title="Q: How big the scale of the company needs to be that you will work with it? Do you accept requests from SMBs or only from big corporations? " open_toggle_background_color="#2da5ee" open_toggle_text_color="#ffffff" closed_toggle_background_color="#333333" closed_toggle_text_color="#ffffff" icon_color="#ffffff"]<p><span style="color: #2da5ee;">A:&nbsp;</span> We''ve never had particularly strict benchmarks on how big a company must be so we can take it onboard. We''ve always welcomed the SMB businesses to become our clients and highlighted, that in the modern competitive rhythm the business world lives and works in, SMBs need our help more than bog corporations do!</p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item][tm_pb_accordion_item title="Q: Do you offer not US based, overseas consulting management? "]<p><span style="color: #2da5ee;">A: </span>Of course. Though our company is registered and based in the US (NYC), we can work with any other jurisdiction or country. Footnote: though the main company still needs to be a US registered one..</p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item][tm_pb_accordion_item title="Q: Do you work in Tax management optimization field? "]<p><span style="color: #2da5ee;">A: </span>No, this is not our field of specialization.</p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item]\n\n[/tm_pb_accordion]', 'accordion_hayford', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'accordion_hayford', '', '', '2016-07-26 08:47:29', '2016-07-26 08:47:29', '', 0, 'your_website_url_here/tm_pb_layout/accordion_hayford/', 0, 'tm_pb_layout', '', 0),
