(1234, 1, '2016-07-26 11:39:15', '2016-07-26 11:39:15', '[tm_pb_tabs admin_label="Tabs" active_tab_background_color="#2da5ee" inactive_tab_background_color="#333333" tab_text_color="#ffffff" use_border_color="on" border_color="#ebebeb" border_style="solid" tab_font="Merriweather|on|||" tab_font_size="16" body_font_size="16" saved_tabs="all" template_type="module"]\n\n[tm_pb_tab title="Assessment" tab_font_select="default" tab_font="||||" tab_line_height="2em" tab_line_height_tablet="2em" tab_line_height_phone="2em" body_font_select="default" body_font="||||" body_line_height="2em" body_line_height_tablet="2em" body_line_height_phone="2em"]<p>Firstly we received access to all documentation, reports and structure of the company. We analyzed the current and yearly performance, sales, staff flow for the hayford company...&nbsp;<img class="size-full wp-image-1192 aligncenter" src="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/tabs01.jpg" alt="tabs01" height="586" width="1098"></p>[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title="Business strategy" tab_font_select="default" tab_font="||||" tab_line_height="2em" tab_line_height_tablet="2em" tab_line_height_phone="2em" body_font_select="default" body_font="||||" body_line_height="2em" body_line_height_tablet="2em" body_line_height_phone="2em"]<p>The next step was to draft a business strategy for business'' future deelopment over a period of 2, 5 and 10 years. We always aim to correlate our recommendations with the vision each company offers, when we''re composing such a strategy... <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-75" src="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img09.jpg" alt="img09" height="853" width="1280"></p>[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title="HR optimization" tab_font_select="default" tab_font="||||" tab_line_height="2em" tab_line_height_tablet="2em" tab_line_height_phone="2em" body_font_select="default" body_font="||||" body_line_height="2em" body_line_height_tablet="2em" body_line_height_phone="2em"]<p>An optimized business always starts with the team optimization. That is the reason we do the human resources diligence and file our suggestions to the board. <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-77" src="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img01.jpg" alt="img01" height="854" width="1280"></p>[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title="Processes optimization" tab_font_select="default" tab_font="||||" tab_line_height="2em" tab_line_height_tablet="2em" tab_line_height_phone="2em" body_font_select="default" body_font="||||" body_line_height="2em" body_line_height_tablet="2em" body_line_height_phone="2em"]<p>Business processes optimization is the most vital instrument when we aim to turn the company around. We always sketch and implement such overhauls in a close cooperation with company''s top management. <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-73" src="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img07.jpg" alt="img07" height="853" width="1280"></p>[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title="Market research" tab_font_select="default" tab_font="||||" tab_line_height="2em" tab_line_height_tablet="2em" tab_line_height_phone="2em" body_font_select="default" body_font="||||" body_line_height="2em" body_line_height_tablet="2em" body_line_height_phone="2em"]<p>Being one of the most competitive out there, we had conducted multiple researches and we arranged an extensive overhaul for the marketing department of the company. <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-69" src="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img03.jpg" alt="img03" height="854" width="1280"></p>[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title="Year-by-year analysis" tab_font_select="default" tab_font="||||" tab_line_height="2em" tab_line_height_tablet="2em" tab_line_height_phone="2em" body_font_select="default" body_font="||||" body_line_height="2em" body_line_height_tablet="2em" body_line_height_phone="2em"]<p>After out initial job''s been implemented, the next thing we did is a year-by-year analysis. Since year one and during all 6 years we''ve been advising hayford company shown a significant surge both in sales and market value. <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-81" src="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img11.jpg" alt="img11" height="853" width="1280"></p>[/tm_pb_tab]\n\n[/tm_pb_tabs]', 'tabs_hayford', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tabs_hayford', '', '', '2016-07-26 11:39:15', '2016-07-26 11:39:15', '', 0, 'your_website_url_here/tm_pb_layout/tabs_hayford/', 0, 'tm_pb_layout', '', 0),
