="off" text_orientation="center" use_icon_font_size="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" header_text_color="#2da5ee" custom_margin="||60px|" custom_margin_tablet="||30px|" custom_margin_last_edited="on|tablet" url="your_website_url_here/cases/strong/"]\n\n<p>An all-American chain, that recovered after dropping in sales in 2008 and since then returned great year-by-year growth...</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type="1_3"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label="Blurb" title="Smart One" url_new_window="off" use_icon="off" icon_color="#49d376" use_circle="off" circle_color="#333333" use_circle_border="off" circle_border_color="#49d376" image="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/logo05.png" icon_placement="top" animation="off" text_orientation="center" use_icon_font_size="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" header_text_color="#2da5ee" custom_margin="||60px|" custom_margin_tablet="||30px|" custom_margin_last_edited="on|tablet" url="your_website_url_here/cases/smart-one/"]\n\n<p>An online service unlike any other, which we helped to sketch out and put to action a comprehensive investment planning for.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type="1_3"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label="Blurb" title="Aqua" url_new_window="off" use_icon="off" icon_color="#49d376" use_circle="off" circle_color="#333333" use_circle_border="off" circle_border_color="#49d376" image="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/logo06.png" icon_placement="top" animation="off" text_orientation="center" use_icon_font_size="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" header_text_color="#2da5ee" custom_margin="||60px|" custom_margin_tablet="||30px|" custom_margin_last_edited="on|tablet" url="your_website_url_here/cases/aqua/"]\n\n<p>General Motors suffered a severe setback in sales and overall market value. We, together with the US govt helped to diverge the fiscal disaster.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label="Row" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" use_grid_padding="on" width_unit="on" padding_mobile="off" custom_margin_last_edited="on|tablet" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" make_equal="off" parallax_1="off" parallax_method_1="off" parallax_2="off" parallax_method_2="off" parallax_3="off" parallax_method_3="off" column_padding_mobile="on"][tm_pb_column type="1_3"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label="Blurb" title="Olio Company" url_new_window="off" use_icon="off" icon_color="#49d376" use_circle="off" circle_color="#333333" use_circle_border="off" circle_border_color="#49d376" image="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/logo07.png" icon_placement="top" animation="off" text_orientation="center" use_icon_font_size="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" header_text_color="#2da5ee" custom_margin="||60px|" custom_margin_tablet="||30px|" custom_margin_last_edited="on|tablet" url="your_website_url_here/cases/olio-company/"]\n\n<p>Manufacturer trucks and offers a broad range of services for the over-the-road, construction, municipal and medium duty markets.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type="1_3"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label="Blurb" title="Richard White" url_new_window="off" use_icon="off" icon_color="#49d376" use_circle="off" circle_color="#333333" use_circle_border="off" circle_border_color="#49d376" image="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/logo08.png" icon_placement="top" animation="off" text_orientation="center" use_icon_font_size="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" header_text_color="#2da5ee" custom_margin="||60px|" custom_margin_tablet="||30px|" custom_margin_last_edited="on|tablet" url="your_website_url_here/cases/richard-white/"]\n\n<p>BenQ Corporation is a Taiwanese multi-national company that sells and markets technology products, consumer electronics, computing.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type="1_3"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label="Blurb" title="Compact" url_new_window="off" use_icon="off" icon_color="#49d376" use_circle="off" circle_color="#333333" use_circle_border="off" circle_border_color="#49d376" image="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/logo09.png" icon_placement="top" animation="off" text_orientation="center" use_icon_font_size="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" header_text_color="#2da5ee" custom_margin="||60px|" custom_margin_tablet="||30px|" custom_margin_last_edited="on|tablet" url="your_website_url_here/cases/compact/"]\n\n<p>Compaq was a company founded in 1982, offerings include Presario notebooks and laptop PCs, desktops and computer accessories.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label="Row" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" use_grid_padding="on" width_unit="on" padding_mobile="off" custom_margin_last_edited="on|tablet" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" make_equal="off" parallax_1="off" parallax_method_1="off" parallax_2="off" parallax_method_2="off" parallax_3="off" parallax_method_3="off" column_padding_mobile="on"][tm_pb_column type="1_3"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label="Blurb" title="Bingo" url_new_window="off" use_icon="off" icon_color="#49d376" use_circle="off" circle_color="#333333" use_circle_border="off" circle_border_color="#49d376" image="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/logo10.png" icon_placement="top" animation="off" text_orientation="center" use_icon_font_size="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" header_text_color="#2da5ee" custom_margin="||60px|" custom_margin_tablet="||30px|" custom_margin_last_edited="on|tablet" url="your_website_url_here/cases/bingo/"]\n\n<p>That''s just one of the hardware/software industry leaders whom we consult on business strategic planning...</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type="1_3"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label="Blurb" title="Be Clener" url_new_window="off" use_icon="off" icon_color="#49d376" use_circle="off" circle_color="#333333" use_circle_border="off" circle_border_color="#49d376" image="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/logo11.png" icon_placement="top" animation="off" text_orientation="center" use_icon_font_size="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" header_text_color="#2da5ee" custom_margin="||60px|" custom_margin_tablet="||30px|" custom_margin_last_edited="on|tablet" url="your_website_url_here/cases/be-clener/"]\n\n<p>Maxdata was a German company that produced IT products, such as computers, notebooks and monitors.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type="1_3"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label="Blurb" title="Domino" url_new_window="off" use_icon="off" icon_color="#49d376" use_circle="off" circle_color="#333333" use_circle_border="off" circle_border_color="#49d376" image="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/logo12.png" icon_placement="top" animation="off" text_orientation="center" use_icon_font_size="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" header_text_color="#2da5ee" custom_margin="||60px|" custom_margin_tablet="||30px|" custom_margin_last_edited="on|tablet" url="your_website_url_here/cases/domino/"]\n\n<p>It''s one of our oldest returning clients. Their year-by-year growth, achieved in big part thanks to our advice, is the reason.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section]', 'cases_hayford', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cases_hayford', '', '', '2016-07-26 15:50:22', '2016-07-26 15:50:22', '', 0, 'your_website_url_here/tm_pb_layout/cases_hayford/', 0, 'tm_pb_layout', '', 0),
