es to stock exchange and insurance bonds...</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type="1_4"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label="Blurb" title="Taxes, Estate and Property" url_new_window="off" use_icon="off" icon_color="#49d376" use_circle="off" circle_color="#333333" use_circle_border="off" circle_border_color="#49d376" icon_placement="top" animation="top" text_orientation="center" use_icon_font_size="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" image="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/icon03-1.png" custom_margin="||60px|" custom_margin_last_edited="on|tablet" custom_margin_tablet="||30px|" url="your_website_url_here/services/taxes-estate-and-property/"]\n\n<p>Managing all the fiscal risks that relate to paying your taxes, owning a real estate or any other property is what we''re provenly good at!</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type="1_4"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label="Blurb" title="Retirement Planning Management" url_new_window="off" use_icon="off" icon_color="#49d376" use_circle="off" circle_color="#333333" use_circle_border="off" circle_border_color="#49d376" icon_placement="top" animation="top" text_orientation="center" use_icon_font_size="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" image="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/icon04-1.png" custom_margin="||60px|" custom_margin_last_edited="on|tablet" custom_margin_tablet="||30px|" url="your_website_url_here/services/retirement-planning-management/ "]\n\n<p>Planning a retirement mustn''t be a hasty process. We take a diligent approach to that matter, planning a beforehand, all-out  retirement schemes...</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row]', 'services_hayford', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'services_hayford', '', '', '2016-07-29 14:10:30', '2016-07-29 14:10:30', '', 0, 'your_website_url_here/tm_pb_layout/services_hayford/', 0, 'tm_pb_layout', '', 0),
